    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/bac788f61d3b7394f9a6de949a528b6e.poster.avif?t=1739777305\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/bac788f61d3b7394f9a6de949a528b6e.webm?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/bac788f61d3b7394f9a6de949a528b6e.mp4?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>白金工作室的 NEO-CLASSIC ARCADE 系列采用现代技术，延续了经典游戏的精神和乐趣，该系列的首个项目就是《SOL CRESTA》。《SOL CRESTA》采用了经典射击游戏《Moon Cresta》和《Terra Cresta》的首尾衔接和合体编队策略，并以“自由对接”系统对两者进行升华。旗舰“大和号”由三艘组合战舰“天照号”、“月读号”、“须佐之男号”组成，可根据三艘战舰的不同排列方式，利用各种攻击方式与敌人战斗。合体、分离并重新排列三艘战舰是击退“超巨佐菲尔”侵略军的关键。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>剧情</strong><br>曼德勒外星大军入侵了太阳系，人类面临着灭亡的悲惨命运。失守月球，又被逐出地球，人类被迫一路撤退到海卫十二。抱着最后一丝希望，幸存的人类组成了太阳系救援队 SOL CRESTA，并将太阳系最终的命运托付给了尖端科技的对接战舰“大和号”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/f36786e542d7804bda40408e72c62910.poster.avif?t=1739777305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/f36786e542d7804bda40408e72c62910.webm?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/f36786e542d7804bda40408e72c62910.mp4?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>自由衔接组合</strong><br>抗击“超巨佐菲尔”邪恶势力的旗舰“大和号”由 3 艘战舰组合而成。游戏开始时，你只能操纵一艘战舰出击，但在拾取合适道具后，会有更多友军战舰出现，提升你的战力！组合和分离能改变你的攻击属性，使用不同的编队来获取惊人的火力武装。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/23904f490a99b0821e14b8131fa04934.poster.avif?t=1739777305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/23904f490a99b0821e14b8131fa04934.webm?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/23904f490a99b0821e14b8131fa04934.mp4?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>经典的 80 年代情怀</strong><br>《SOL CRESTA》的配乐由传奇芯片音乐作曲家古代祐三打造，游戏向早期 Cresta 系列游戏的声音及视觉效果致敬，超越了单纯的怀旧，带你重温往日的街机狂热。甚至还有限时高分大篷车模式和在线排行榜。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/0ef99425f52cb761c573bd9922e8e7c6.poster.avif?t=1739777305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/0ef99425f52cb761c573bd9922e8e7c6.webm?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575640/extras/0ef99425f52cb761c573bd9922e8e7c6.mp4?t=1739777305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>白金工作室的新挑战</strong><br>白金工作室曾经开发过许多充满乐趣、刺激紧张的动作游戏，如《猎天使魔女》《尼尔：自动人形》和《异界锁链》。但如果他们尝试去开发一款射击游戏会怎么样呢？这就是答案。具有经典的视觉效果，同时系统的独创性、深度以及游戏玩法又提供了一种新鲜而深刻的射击游戏体验，这种体验在每次游戏过程中都会不断加深。</li></ul>",
